{"tid":662463,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文,求助] whatsapp回復備份失敗","createTime":"2018-05-12T12:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T15:30:06.000Z","uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2f045382f63b5f09d01c24692eac172bea4eaf6c","tid":662463,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"我部LG因為mon出事, 求其買部小米頂住先, 用番本身既sim卡/電話number<br />\n我跟正常程序, 將ws備份google drive, 然後係新機裝ws, 電話number認證, 收sms, 再回復備份<br />\n<br />\n問題出現了...<br />\n上載+下載備份冇問題, 但去到'正在回復訊息 X%', 硬係卡撚住, <br />\n然後就話: &quot;無法從此備份檔回復對話, 想從舊備份回復資料嗎?&quot;  略過or 從舊備份回復<br />\n略過, 就無哂對話紀錄....... 從舊備份回復, 就卡住係正在回復訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更慘既係, 因為我不停嘗試, reinstall ws太多次, 係咁用電話認證, 等下次既時間倍級增長, 而家要我等1日後先可以再認證過 (下次就2日後..dllm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  )<br />\n<br />\n網上有幾種方法:<br />\n1. 係舊機ws 重新備份過 (failed)<br />\n2. 駁舊機落電腦, 將成個ws file copy and paste去新機 (failed)<br />\n3. google drive delete備份先, 再跟正常程序做 (未試)<br />\n4. root機 (未試)<br />\n5. copy去sd card (未試)<br />\n6. rename backup file (未試)<br />\n最大問題係試呢d方法要reinstall ws, 等下次電話認證, 真係等到人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想問有冇連登expert有解決方法, 無限感激 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fe44e07b715650718334f7f06b7297212d8c94","tid":662463,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddb47a16ca9b325ada3b1ee3b004499c9d20c0e","tid":662463,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:13:19.000Z","msg":"冇得搞，轉電話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec50f600af6958c0972941aff12cfb4677427c53","tid":662463,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cddb4